title: CMIP6 Interactive Visualization
description: Project created during DSC106 to design an interactive visualization based on CMIP6 simulated climate data.

title: Persuasive/Deceptive Visualization
description: Project created during DSC106 to design two visualizations arguing for and against a proposition, leveraging both earnest and deceptive visualization techniques.

title: Forma
description: A computer vision powered basketball training app, aimed towards helping users adjust their shooting forms and dribbling moves to match their favorite players.

title: Summoner Insights
description: An end-to-end data science project made during DSC80 to produce a predictive model for determining which factors most influence winning in professional League of Legends.

title: Bikewatching
description: An interactive geospatial visualization of bike traffic in the Boston Area, created during lab 7 of DSC 106.
